Package: bayescheck
Title: Automatically Extract Statistics from Articles and Compute Bayes Factors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Marton', 'Kovacs', email = 'marton.balazs.kovacs@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: The aim of the package is to search the text of scientific articles /
                     for statistical tests and compute the evidential value /
                     based on Bayes factors. The package is based on the 'statcheck' package.
